                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The amount of time required to prepare for the CISM exam depends on how much you already know about the certification domains. That’s why its generally considered a good idea to enroll for a CISM prep course to help get you up to speed on all exam concepts. Doing so will help you cut your CISM certification preparation time significantly than if you were to prepare by yourself.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-21">21. What are the best books for CISM Exam preparation?</a> </div>
