                                            <p>Once you have gained the CISM Certification, you can consider pursuing the following courses: </p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>CGEIT—Certified in the Governance of Enterprise IT</li>
                                                <li>CSX-P—Cybersecurity Practitioner Certification</li>
                                            </ul>
